        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/462/280/medium/8f35d1f7-d175-4e5a-8256-95bd522b06d2.png" srcset="" alt="View Course Font" height="413" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_b207a161-bcec-4dce-b032-2424650f9ecc" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Canvas displays a new font, Balsamiq Sans, in the Global Navigation Menu [1], Course Navigation Menu [2], and Breadcrumbs bar [3]. Â </p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> If the feature preview is turned off, the font changes from Balsamiq Sans to the Canvas default, Lato.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view-rich-content-editor" data-step-uuid="271c0c64-779b-4f74-bc10-b4a4a8210796">
