        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/462/281/original/dba77154-cec8-4b90-bbef-7331ee682ff3.png" srcset="" alt="View Rich Content Editor" height="390" width="769">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_6af9a1a5-abbe-41c1-88c9-bd632686b63a" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The Balsamiq Sans font also displays in the Rich Content Editor [1]. You can also select the font Architect's Daughter from the Format menu in the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-menubar-in-the-Rich-Content-Editor-as-an/ta-p/931" target="_blank">menubar</a> [2].</p>
